snippet.title: Duck Life 9 Trailer - Welcome to the flock!
snippet.description:
WISHLIST THE GAME ON STEAM HERE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2416880?utm_source=yt

Get ready for a quacking good time in Duck Life 9: The Flock! Embark on an egg-citing adventure as you craft your very own village, nurture a feathery fleet of ducks, and turbocharge your way to becoming the undisputed champion racer! 🐥🏁

Sail over to the sun-soaked paradise of Featherhaven Island where the waves are high, and the energy is higher! Rub feathers with the locals, paddle your way through thrilling tournaments, and seize the chance to rake in riches and bask in the glow of glory! 🏆🌴

So, what are you waiting for? Grab your goggles, fluff up those feathers, and let's dive headfirst into the most feather-ruffling, splash-making, webbed-feet racing extravaganza you've ever seen!

Duck Life 9 is releasing for PC/Mac/iOS/Android/Switch/Xbox/PS5 in early 2024

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/MAPEkNB4sC
Read the dev logs: https://games.wixgames.co.uk/dl9-devlogs/
